parameters: ????: Have you made it this far...

????: Those who have defeated the Star
God and been entrusted with guiding the
future, \c[6]the last hope\c[0],
gather.

????: Lala... Thank goodness you've made
it this far...

Lala: I've been searching... searching
for a long time...

Lala: I've always believed that Lady Ern
is alive...

Lala: Why... didn't you come to see
me...?

Lala: It's because you... hate me,
right...?

Lala: If I were stronger, Lady Ern
would...

Ern: I'm not as great of an angel as you
think...

Ern: When my heart was pierced by
Sariel, I realized my own weakness.
Ern: More than my own life, Lala...

Ern: Because I was able to save the life
of my dear friend, I am still proud...

Ern: The strength you gained over the
long time since losing me has become
real, and you defeated the Star God.

Ern: You will be fine on your own. With
this, I can leave without any worries.

Ern: ...Some things never change, like
being a crybaby.

Lala: Lady Ern, you... you're trying to
disappear on your own...

Ern: Now is not the time to rejoice in
our reunion.
Ern: The true calamity is yet to come.

Zerachiel: What do you mean? We should
have defeated the Star God...

Ern: The Star God is just the beginning,
Zerachiel...

Ern: I am Ern... Former Archangel and
the leader of the angels.
Claudia: I've heard the story from Lala.

Claudia: More importantly, what do you
mean by the calamity that is about to
come?

Ern: It means exactly what it says,
Claudia.

Ern: In the near future... this world
will meet its end.
Ern: By the God of the New Era...

Rabi: I have absolutely no idea what
you're talking about, you know??

Ern: It's natural that you don't
understand, Sachia, Rabi...

Ern: Even the fact that I am alive is a
great sin...

Ern: If I were to tell you that this
moment is a world where \c[6]everything
can be redone\c[0], would you believe
me?

Zerachiel: A world where everything can
be redone...
Claudia: ...I can't believe it at all.
Ern: Please take a look at this.
Zerachiel: I sense a strong element...

Claudia: ...This is a holy relic. My
mother had the same one.

Claudia: Is there something wrong with
this?

Ern: This is a holy relic called the
\c[6]celestial globe\c[0].

Ern: It is rumored that \c[6]time\c[0]
is imbued with the power to interfere...

Ern: When the power to interfere with
\c[6]coordinates\c[0] combines...

Ern: I will obtain the power to \c[0]go
back to the past\c[0].

Zerachiel: The power to go back to the
past...

Rabi: I can't believe it no matter
what...

Ern: If an evil person were to obtain
this power, they would reshape the world
into their ideal...

Ern: For example, when the Star God goes
back to the past, it is also possible
for it to branch off into a future where
it defeats all of you.

Claudia: ...That is an impossible feat
even for a god.
Ern: But, I can't deny it.

Ern: ...All of us have been helped by
this power.

Ern: You have been helped many times,
you know.
Ern: Do you remember fragments of it?

Ern: Already, although on a very small
scale, the alteration of this world is
taking place.

Ern: In order to redo the fact that we
were defeated by the \c[6]God of the New
Era\c[0] and the world was destroyed.
Ern: At first... I was your enemy.

Ern: Because of that, we clashed many
times and couldn't notice the gods
lurking behind the Star God.

Ern: We, who were defeated, used the
power of the celestial globe that
interferes with \c[6]time\c[0] to go
back to the past.

Ern: As a result, I rebelled against the
Star God and ended up confronting
Sariel...

Ern: As a result, we ended up defeating
the Star God early on...

Ern: Originally, the possibility of
altering the future that was supposed to
be destroyed has emerged.

Lala: It doesn't seem like you're
lying...
Ern: I shamefully managed to survive.

Ern: And so, I was entrusted with the
future by my comrades.

Ern: Originally, I planned to tell you
the truth and leave...
Ern: I want to give it a try.
Ern: Let me give you all a trial.

Ern: I am the guardian of paradise,
Ern...

Ern: A wretched existence who was saved
by the divine beast Artemis and survived
at the cost of everything...

Ern: The weight of countless defeats in
the future, and the strength of your
bonds... which one is stronger...

Ern: Shall we confirm it by giving our
all to each other?

Lala: Ern-sama, I'm coming at you with
all my might...!!
Claudia: I'll show you our power...!

Sachia: All living things will
eventually die, but we can also resist,
right?

Rabi: No matter what kind of future
awaits, I will choose my own place to
die!

Ern: Come at me. Oh chosen ones guided
by the stars.

Ern: These are the ones who defeated the
Star God...
Ern: Is this the last hope...?
Ern: Hehe, I certainly witnessed it.

Ern: If it's you all, you might be able
to change the future.

Zerachiel: Even though you said you were
serious, it felt like you were holding
back...

Ern: Through the battle just now, I
realized that I can trust all of you.

Ern: ...From now on, there may be a long
and difficult reality waiting.

Ern: Even so, if it's all of you... I
believe we can overcome it.

Lala: If that's the case, please take me
with you too...!

Ern: Lala, even if you're not worried,
it's okay.

Ern: Treasure your comrades and lend a
hand when they're in trouble.

Lala: The next time we meet, I'll show
you how much stronger I've become!!

Lala: Even without relying on Ern-sama's
power, I will become strong enough to
protect everyone!

Ern: Surely, I will become an angel more
splendid than anyone else...

Claudia: It seems like they were waiting
for us to come.
Rabi: You seemed happy to see Lala.

Zerachiel: (Because I was really
reluctant to part ways)

Lala: I will become strong. I will show
everyone that I can become a splendid
angel more than anyone else.

Lala: \c[6]The god of a new era\c[0], I
don't know who they are...

Lala: I will definitely overcome it and
show everyone.

Claudia: It's going to be tough from now
on, but I feel like we can overcome it
if we're together.
Sachia: We have to do our best too.
Zerachiel: Well then, shall we go home?

Zerachiel: To Logres, where everyone is
waiting.

Zerachiel: No, I can't win... I have to
become stronger...
